{"tid":1618718,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[警告] 就算上唔到連登，都唔好上 Reddit ！！！","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:14:43.000Z","uid":59440,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3739343ff41d3ab1bcda8fc814a543640bdd7c1a","tid":1618718,"uid":59440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Reddit 確定獲騰訊投資 1.5 億美元</strong></span>，網友狂貼天安門事件照反擊<br />\n<br />\n2 月初傳出美國社群平台 Reddit 將從中國科技巨頭騰訊募資 1.5 億美元的消息，如今這項傳聞獲得證實，引起大量 Reddit 用戶不滿，擔憂 Reddit 會加強言論管制。<br />\n<br />\nReddit 這次共募資 3 億美元，其中 1.5 億美元由騰訊出資。募資案將讓 Reddit 的總募資金額達 5.5 億美元，除了本次加入的騰訊，之前的投資者還包括紅杉資本、Conde Nast、富達和 Andreessen Horowitz 等公司。根據科技媒體 TechCrunch 報導，消息來源指出 Reddit 在 2018 年營收為 8,500 萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n中國網路長城的幫兇投資美國言論自由最猖狂的論壇之一，讓人感到說不出的詭異，騰訊更於 2018 年在中國幫助封鎖 Reddit，自然引起 Reddit 用戶對騰訊入股後可能會管制言論的疑慮。從消息傳出開始許多用戶便用張貼各種會激怒中國政府的圖片來抗議這次募資案，包括六四天安門事件的屠殺照片和著名的「坦克人」照片，或是支持台灣獨立和西藏獨立的內容，以及暗諷中國國家主席習近平的小熊維尼圖片。<br />\n<br />\nReddit 每個月有 3.3 億用戶，討論版的範圍從新聞、政治、體制、娛樂到色情都有。雖然用戶數龐大但多數為匿名用戶，且 Reddit 在廣告收入不得不和 Google 及 Facebook 兩個強勁對手競爭。<br />\n<br />\n用戶自然擔心 Reddit 的政策會因騰訊入股而緊縮，但 Reddit 本身也苦惱於平衡言論自由和管制惡意言論之間的平衡，甚至 2015 年爆發過 20 萬網友連署逼臨時執行長鮑康如（Ellen Pao）下台事件。如果大筆資金挹注能幫助 Reddit 找到更有經驗的領導人和更多適合的管理人員，或許能更有效拿捏兩者。但如果缺乏適當的監督，即使多了 3 億美元資金，也無法解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/02/12/reddit-confirm-150-million-us-dollar-investment-from-tencent/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F02%2F12%2Freddit-confirm-150-million-us-dollar-investment-from-tencent%2F&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3vFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=b14ff431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/02/12/reddit-confirm-150-million-us-dollar-investment-from-tencent/</a>"},{"pid":"0a656437f29ec11311a5102de3fe645e74071858","tid":1618718,"uid":59440,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:24:45.000Z","msg":"被迫要轉就轉 Twitter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73add6d5f0df540f03bf3115f745dda47fecc4e8","tid":1618718,"uid":59440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有高登都唔安全</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20141029/s00001/1414589018544/紐時-警曾要求高登交用戶資料\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20141029%2Fs00001%2F1414589018544%2F%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82-%E8%AD%A6%E6%9B%BE%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BB%E4%BA%A4%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3vFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=5e9ce6aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20141029%2Fs00001%2F1414589018544%2F%E7%B4%90%E6%99%82-%E8%AD%A6%E6%9B%BE%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BB%E4%BA%A4%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99&h=028f39e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20141029/s00001/1414589018544/紐時-警曾要求高登交用戶資料</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林祖舜指，曾經簽署一份協議，指當警方的前提是調查或防止罪案發生，個人資料私隱條例就不適用。</span></span>"},{"pid":"64c126e0327537b245aa9366636afaec8be00e1c","tid":1618718,"uid":59440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:26:41.000Z","msg":"推啊屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c729552a8202b586368d5e0ead8ee1beefd723f3","tid":1618718,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兵貴神速 今晚就要先聲奪人！</span></span>"},{"pid":"867e454aaaddce8dc54fb7309fc48c2f47c33d28","tid":1618718,"uid":78087,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"又黎，我屌你老母<br />\n冇上開reddit就咪撚on9啦<br />\n果時有依個消息一出，Redditor係嬲到係極多subs放64反共野<br /